    <p class="mb-3">
      The Standard Plan is a <strong>one-step evaluation</strong> with no time limits and a minimum of <strong>four trading days</strong> required to pass. Once you meet the objectives, you can get funded with up to $150,000 in simulated capital. A <strong>$125 activation fee</strong> applies when transitioning to a funded account.
